        ("Multiple Choice:", "A spacecraft needs 6 km/s of delta-v to reach Asteroid A (C-type, water-rich) and 9 km/s to reach Asteroid B (M-type, platinum-rich). If fuel requirements increase exponentially with delta-v, which statement best describes the cost comparison? A) Asteroid B costs 50% more, B) Asteroid B costs 3-5x more, C) Asteroid B costs about the same, D) The cost depends only on asteroid size"),
